    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >DLC总计九个建筑外观，内含：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >瑞鹤图：飘飘元是三山侣，两两还呈千岁姿。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >文化建筑-长明殿-瑞鹤图（珍绝）</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >木石心系列：有木石心，不为外物扰。危坐如故，若无所闻。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >商业建筑-华服店-木石心（极其稀有）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >手工建筑-织布坊-木石心（非常稀有）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >手工建筑-染坊-木石心（非常稀有）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >手工建筑-布庄-木石心（稀有）</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >个个竹系列：江南百姓喜竹屋，竹成个个，个个竹。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >商业建筑-酒楼-个个竹（极其稀有）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >手工建筑-酿酒坊-个个竹（非常稀有）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >商业建筑-酒馆-个个竹（稀有）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >手工建筑-磨坊-个个竹（稀有）</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>注：建筑外观使用方式：</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332130/extras/79121946e6e01bffacefc4409f8ddff5.avif?t=1738112499\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332130/extras_big/79121946e6e01bffacefc4409f8ddff5.avif?t=1738112499 width=800 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332130/extras/90d35b9f7a419bd868d4ef1dd840bc52.avif?t=1738112499\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332130/extras_big/90d35b9f7a419bd868d4ef1dd840bc52.avif?t=1738112499 width=800 height=450 /></span></p>",
